S T A T E O F R H O D E I S L A N D
IN GENERAL ASSEMBLY
JANUARY SESSION, A.D. 2025
____________
H O U S E R E S O L U T I O N
AMENDING THE RULES OF THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES FOR THE YEARS
2023 AND 2024
Introduced By: Representative David J. Place
Date Introduced: January 10, 2025
Referred To: House Rules
1 RESOLVED, that section 37(a) of the rules of the House of Representatives adopted by
2 the House of Representatives at its January session, A.D. 2023, entitled “House Resolution
3 Adopting the Rules of the House of Representatives for the years 2023 and 2024”, be and the
4 same is hereby amended to read as follows:
5 (37)(a) The presiding officer may refer to "Mason's Manual of Legislative Procedure,"
6 most recent edition, published by the National Conference of State Legislatures, for guidance as
7 to procedure on the floor of the House in all cases in which its provisions are not inconsistent
8 with applicable law or these rules. The presiding officer shall publish and make available to the
9 House, a compilation of House procedure which is not addressed in either these rules or in
10 "Mason's Manual of Legislative Procedure."
